<bioghist encodinganalog="545">
<p>Methodist Episcopal minister who ministered in Detroit and Ann Arbor, Michigan and Evanston, Illinois.</p>
</bioghist>

<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
<p>The collection is arranged into three small series: Correspondence, Studley Family, and Other Papers. Included in the collection is a scattering of correspondence, diaries, 1860 and 1873, of trip in Florida and Europe, a scrapbook, and newspaper clippings concerning the activities of the Studley family, 1855-1910.</p>
</scopecontent>

